description: This library creates a 6 digit seven segment LED style display on a 20x4 LCD display. The segments are activated by boolean logic.
name: lcd-i2c-20x4-seven-segment-emulator

SyPbE_WrL.description: Three column block where  number will  display. (1-6 starting on right)
SyPbE_WrL.label: Block

rk61fObrI.description: When true, the decimal point will display in the lower right corner of this character.
rk61fObrI.label: DEC
